#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.1"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.1:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.1:0.2"
msgid "1. Samādhivagga"
msgstr "1. Immersion"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.1:0.3"
msgid "1. Samādhisutta"
msgstr "1. Immersion"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.414"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.1:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn56.1:1.2"
msgid "… pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn56.1:1.3"
msgid "“Samādhiṃ, bhikkhave, bhāvetha."
msgstr "“Mendicants, develop immersion."

msgctxt "sn56.1:1.4"
msgid "Samāhito, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr "A mendicant who has immersion truly understands."

msgctxt "sn56.1:1.5"
msgid "Kiñca yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti?"
msgstr "What do they truly understand?"

msgctxt "sn56.1:1.6"
msgid ""
"‘Idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ‘ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo’ti yathābhūtaṃ "
"pajānāti, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr ""
"They truly understand: ‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin of "
"suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice "
"that leads to the cessation of suffering’."

msgctxt "sn56.1:1.7"
msgid "Samādhiṃ, bhikkhave, bhāvetha."
msgstr "Develop immersion."

msgctxt "sn56.1:1.8"
msgid "Samāhito, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr "A mendicant who has immersion truly understands."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.1:2.1"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo, ‘ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo’"
"ti yogo karaṇīyo, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’ti yogo karaṇīyo, ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s why you should practice meditation to understand: ‘This is suffering’ "
"… ‘This is the origin of suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … "
"‘This is the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering’.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.1:2.2"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
